Name: team_assigned_to_project
Description: 1 if Team is assigned to Project; 0 otherwise

Name: worker_belongs_to_team
Description: 1 if Worker belongs to Team; 0 otherwise

Name: worker_takes_role
Description: 1 if Worker takes a Role; 0 otherwise

Name: po_manages_product_backlog
Description: 1 if Product Owner manages Product Backlog; 0 otherwise

Name: scrum_master_supports_team
Description: 1 if Scrum Master supports Team; 0 otherwise

Name: product_backlog_contains_feature
Description: 1 if Product Backlog contains Feature; 0 otherwise

Name: product_backlog_contains_epic
Description: 1 if Product Backlog contains Epic; 0 otherwise

Name: epic_contains_user_story
Description: 1 if Epic contains User Story; 0 otherwise

Name: user_story_consists_of_task
Description: 1 if User Story consists of Task; 0 otherwise

Name: user_story_in_sprint_backlog
Description: 1 if User Story is in Sprint Backlog; 0 otherwise

Name: sprint_backlog_in_sprint
Description: 1 if Sprint Backlog belongs to Sprint; 0 otherwise

Name: sprint_pursues_goal
Description: 1 if Sprint pursues a Sprint Goal; 0 otherwise

Name: task_blocked_by_blocker
Description: 1 if Task is blocked by Blocker; 0 otherwise

Name: velocity_refers_to_team
Description: 1 if Velocity record refers to Team; 0 otherwise
